Friday the petition had been filed in <LOCATION> U.S. </LOCATION> <ORGANIZATION> Bankruptcy </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Court </ORGANIZATION>, southern district of <LOCATION> New </LOCATION> <LOCATION> York </LOCATION>.
